        <item>
            <title>中国网民用烂机壳砌机，内装 RTX 4090 总值 3 万成功呃到屋企人</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/12/expensive-diy-parts-in-cheap-box/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=expensive-diy-parts-in-cheap-box</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/12/expensive-diy-parts-in-cheap-box/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 07:00:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[桌上电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[RTX 4090]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旧机箱]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1219408</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>很多男士们购买贵重电子产品、模型都很难入屋，想尽各式奇招，买 PS4 扮买路由器这个笑话也说了很久。而近日中国就有一名网民，利用残破不堪的机箱砌机，里面竟装有最顶尖显示卡 GeForce RTX 4090，总值近 3 万元人民币，最后这部超强电脑却能成功「入屋」。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1219413 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/s_b66a73c161904c2c80-343x580.png" alt="" width="343" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/s_b66a73c161904c2c80-343x580.png 343w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/s_b66a73c161904c2c80.png 532w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 343px" /></p><p>根据中国媒体报道，有一个男子给朋友组装了一部「复古电脑」，外壳所用的胶已严重变黄，更有光碟机这种历史产物。但这个简陋机箱的里面，却装有总值接近 3 万元人民币（约港币 3.26 万元）的 DIY 硬件。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1219412 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/s_b135bacd828f47bfac-385x580.png" alt="" width="385" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/s_b135bacd828f47bfac-385x580.png 385w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/s_b135bacd828f47bfac.png 597w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 385px" /></p><p>一翻开外盖，就可看到电脑里面的布局。一张售价超过 1.2 万港元起跳的 GeForce RTX 4090 显示卡，机箱内装更用上 RGB 装饰的主机板、记忆体、电源线。不过机箱以简陋胶盖覆盖，不像今时今日的电竞电脑有玻璃机盖，这些 RGB 电竞灯饰平时就看不到了。</p><p>网民纷纷称赞事主的头猫，指这部电脑「斯是陋室，威武的芯」、「茅台倒矿泉水瓶」。</p><p>其实以前都有中国网民想到用旧机壳装新机，甚至装得比今次报道的还劲。大家在砌机时可考虑砌一部这样外壳的电脑吧&#8230;</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1219410" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz49dazat3csqoq-582x580.jpg" alt="" width="582" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz49dazat3csqoq-582x580.jpg 582w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz49dazat3csqoq.jpg 903w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz49dazat3csqoq-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 582px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1219411" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz4penzbt3csu0u-579x580.jpg" alt="" width="579" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz4penzbt3csu0u-579x580.jpg 579w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz4penzbt3csu0u.jpg 898w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz4penzbt3csu0u-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 579px" /></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.workercn.cn/c/2024-02-07/8145089.shtml">中工网</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/29/rtx-4090-d/wireless-home/desktop-pc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NVIDIA 中国推降级版 RTX 4090 D    价钱一样但效能较慢</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/19/geforce-rtx-4090-removed-from-official-nvidia-china-websit/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">美国 GeForce RTX 4090 禁令生效　Nvidia 中国官网删除所有相关资料</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/12/expensive-diy-parts-in-cheap-box/fun-tech/">中国网民用烂机壳砌机，内装 RTX 4090 总值 3 万成功呃到屋企人</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
